===荣誉===
在[[第73届奥斯卡金像奖|第73届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中，《毒品网络》获得了[[学院奖最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]、[[学院奖最佳导演奖|导演]]（索德伯格）、[[学院奖最佳原著改编奖|原著改编]]、[[学院奖最佳男配角奖|男配角]]（德尔·托罗）、[[学院奖最佳剪辑奖|剪辑]]5项提名，到了2001年3月25日举行的颁奖典礼上，本片除最后颁发的最佳影片奖不敌[[雷德利·斯科特|雷德利·斯科特]]执导的《[[角斗士_(电影)|角斗士]]》外，其余4个奖项全部胜出<ref name="Oscars2001">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/73rd-winners.html |title=The 73rd Academy Awards (2001) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-11-19 |work=oscars.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924144725/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/73rd-winners.html |archivedate=2014-09-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Rare three-way Oscar scrap |first=John |last=Hartl |url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20010326&slug=hartl260 |work=Seattle Times |date=2001-03-26 |accessdate=2008-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202155257/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20010326&slug=hartl260 |archive-date=2009-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片还获得了5项[[金球奖|金球奖]]提名，包括[[金球奖最佳戏剧类影片|最佳影片（正剧类）]]、[[金球奖最佳导演|导演]]、[[金球奖最佳电影男配角|男配角]]、[[金球奖最佳电影女配角|女配角]]（泽塔-琼斯）、[[金球奖最佳剧本|编剧]]，最终拿下了编剧和男配角两座大奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=/film/25715 |title=Browse Results |publisher=HFPA |accessdate=2013-05-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130704020339/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=/film/25715 |archivedate=2013-07-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Surprises but No Dominator at the Golden Globes |first=Rick |last=Lyman |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950CE1D7133CF931A15752C0A9679C8B63&scp=1&sq=%22Surprises+but+No+Dominator+at+the+Golden+Globes%22&st=nyt |work=The New York Times |date=2001-01-22 |accessdate=2009-02-11}}</ref>。此外，德尔·托罗还获得了[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会]]最佳男主角奖，并与编剧斯蒂芬·加汉分别获得了[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳男配角和最佳改编剧本奖<ref name="Metacrix" />。

[[纽约影评人协会|纽约影评人协会]]将《毒品网络》评选为最佳影片，索德伯格为最佳导演<ref name="Lemons">{{cite news |title=Steven Soderbergh |first=Stephen |last=Lemons |url=http://archive.salon.com/people/conv/2000/12/20/soderbergh |work=Salon.com |date=2000-12-20 |accessdate=2008-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622144348/http://archive.salon.com/people/conv/2000/12/20/soderbergh/ |archive-date=2008-06-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，德尔·托罗获最佳男配角奖<ref>{{cite news |title='Traffic' Captures Awards From New York Film Critics |first=Stephen |last=Holden |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B04EFDC1E3FF937A25751C1A9669C8B63&scp=1&sq=%22Traffic+Captures+Awards+From+New+York+Film+Critics%22&st=nyt |work=The New York Times |date=2000-12-14 |accessdate=2009-02-11}}</ref>。索德伯德也赢得了[[洛杉矶影评人协会|洛杉矶影评人协会]]最佳导演奖<ref>{{cite news |title=L.A. crix take leap with 'Tiger' |first=Todd |last=McCarthy |work=Variety |date=2000-12-18 |accessdate=2012-03-03}}</ref>。[[多伦多影评人协会|多伦多影评人协会]]投票选出索德伯格为最佳导演，德尔·托罗则获最佳男主角奖<ref>{{cite news |title=Toronto Critics Like Lee |first=Peter |last=Howell |work=Toronto Star |date=2000-12-21 |accessdate=2012-03-03}}</ref>。[[国家影评人协会|国家影评人协会]]同样投票选择索德伯格和德尔·托罗分获最佳导演和男配角奖<ref>{{cite news |title=Critics Group Honors Quirky List of Film Favorites |first=Diane |last=Cardwell |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=990CE4D8143AF934A35752C0A9679C8B63&scp=1&sq=%22Critics+Group+Honors+Quirky+List+of+Film+Favorites%22&st=nyt |work=The New York Times |date=2001-01-07 |accessdate=2009-02-11}}</ref>。

